DJ Pierra Makena turned 40 years on Sunday and marked the occasion in style. The mother held a glamorous party at the Emara Ole Sereni Hotel. She invited close friends, family and showbiz personalities to the post event. "Today is my 40th birthday. Caution! I'm on the 4th floor. God has been faithful. Thanks to everyone in my life," she posted on Instagram. The deejay-cum-TV host also thanked her fans for wishing her well. "To everyone who wished me a happy birthday yesterday: Thank you! I had a great day, and hearing from all of you was one of the best parts of it!" Among those who attended her birthday were MC Jessy and comedian Brenda Jones.